1977;;Portrait of a Hitman;;American;;Allan A. Buckhantz;;Rod Steiger, Jack Palance, Bo Svenson;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portrait_of_a_Hitman;;A professional hitman who doubles as a painter is hired to kill a brain surgeon. But it turns out that not only are he and the surgeon are old friends, but they are both in love with the same woman.